595
00:28:04,546 --> 00:28:05,346
I can tell

596
00:28:05,586 --> 00:28:06,746
you really love drawing.

597
00:28:07,466 --> 00:28:08,346
Otherwise,

598
00:28:08,466 --> 00:28:10,666
when you were selling your tablet,

599
00:28:10,666 --> 00:28:11,346
you wouldn't

600
00:28:11,826 --> 00:28:12,826
have hesitated so much.

601
00:28:16,346 --> 00:28:19,066
Actually, I also studied fine arts.

602
00:28:19,466 --> 00:28:20,586
I can see

603
00:28:20,586 --> 00:28:22,346
how strong your fundamentals are.

604
00:28:24,066 --> 00:28:25,066
More importantly,

605
00:28:25,746 --> 00:28:26,746
I can feel

606
00:28:27,186 --> 00:28:29,586
