make drawing your profession, right?

610
00:28:40,066 --> 00:28:41,586
Actually, we really want

611
00:28:41,866 --> 00:28:42,826
to have

612
00:28:43,066 --> 00:28:44,986
an artist as talented as you.

613
00:28:46,426 --> 00:28:46,826
How's it?

614
00:28:48,426 --> 00:28:49,186
Give it a try?

615
00:28:57,706 --> 00:28:59,306
Peng, you are a guest today.

616
00:29:00,826 --> 00:29:02,746
