618
00:29:04,826 --> 00:29:05,546
Take your time.

619
00:29:06,946 --> 00:29:07,946
Thanks, boss.

620
00:29:08,586 --> 00:29:09,066
First,

621
00:29:09,426 --> 00:29:10,866
