622
00:29:11,066 --> 00:29:12,346
the designer Peng.

623
00:29:12,586 --> 00:29:13,306
Welcome.

624
00:29:13,426 --> 00:29:13,826
Welcome.

625
00:29:15,826 --> 00:29:17,106
Then I formally announce

626
00:29:17,346 --> 00:29:18,826
our Gaishi Unparalleled

627
00:29:19,066 --> 00:29:20,226
