636
00:29:37,066 --> 00:29:37,586
Any questions?

637
00:29:37,826 --> 00:29:38,706
No.

638
00:29:38,706 --> 00:29:39,306
Here we go.

639
00:29:39,586 --> 00:29:41,346
Come on.

640
00:29:41,346 --> 00:29:41,746
Cheers.

641
