658
00:30:26,066 --> 00:30:26,826
Leave it to An Ran.

659
00:30:27,066 --> 00:30:27,466
Ran.

660
00:30:27,546 --> 00:30:28,106
- Yes.
- Ran.

661
00:30:28,946 --> 00:30:31,066
Now we have an office,

662
00:30:31,306 --> 00:30:32,866
and we have a full team.

663
00:30:33,826 --> 00:30:34,986
I'm very confident.

664
00:30:35,186 --> 00:30:36,346
I believe Peng's

665
00:30:36,346 --> 00:30:37,986
and all our wishes

666
00:30:38,106 --> 00:30:39,066
