667
00:30:40,346 --> 00:30:41,586
Our game will sell well.

668
00:30:41,826 --> 00:30:43,066
It will definitely happen.

669
00:30:43,346 --> 00:30:44,066
Come on.

670
00:30:44,466 --> 00:30:45,226
