676
00:30:52,866 --> 00:30:53,306
Come on.

677
00:30:55,066 --> 00:30:55,826
Miss An.

678
00:30:56,586 --> 00:30:57,706
I'll show my ambitions today.

679
00:30:58,866 --> 00:30:59,826
Take care.

680
00:31:00,226 --> 00:31:00,746
Careful.

