with three times the salary?

707
00:32:46,506 --> 00:32:47,026
Me too.

708
00:32:48,026 --> 00:32:48,586
And me.

709
00:32:49,106 --> 00:32:50,186
Me as well.

710
00:32:56,706 --> 00:32:57,506
You guys

711
00:32:59,506 --> 00:33:00,106
