717
00:33:21,026 --> 00:33:23,106
I think it's very likely Gaishi Group.

718
00:33:23,746 --> 00:33:24,186
Right, right.

719
00:33:24,466 --> 00:33:25,226
I also think so.

720
00:33:25,746 --> 00:33:27,786
He also knew a lot about
our previous situation.

721
00:33:28,546 --> 00:33:29,946
He must have been
in cahoots with Gaishi Group.

722
00:33:33,266 --> 00:33:33,706
Peng,

723
00:33:34,546 --> 00:33:34,866
