724
00:33:36,026 --> 00:33:36,426
What?

725
00:33:41,266 --> 00:33:42,066
It's okay, Peng.

726
00:33:42,546 --> 00:33:43,746
That you didn't receive an email

727
00:33:43,986 --> 00:33:45,346
