735
00:34:04,666 --> 00:34:05,706
Great, great.

736
00:34:05,706 --> 00:34:06,866
Thank you, Miss An.

737
00:34:08,026 --> 00:34:08,786
Wu,

738
00:34:09,106 --> 00:34:11,026
