for three times the salary, right?

739
00:34:11,026 --> 00:34:11,586
No, no.

740
00:34:11,586 --> 00:34:12,026
Rui.

741
00:34:13,066 --> 00:34:13,986
Hurry up and pack your things.

742
00:34:13,986 --> 00:34:14,666
What are you waiting for?

743
00:34:14,986 --> 00:34:16,306
The holiday has begun.

744
00:34:24,306 --> 00:34:25,026
(Mr. Heisha,)

745
00:34:25,026 --> 00:34:26,546
(we had a clear agreement before.)

746
00:34:26,786 --> 00:34:27,986
(It's a simple matter.)

747
00:34:27,986 --> 00:34:30,066
(If you just turn a blind eye,
