748
00:34:30,946 --> 00:34:32,146
(If I have to follow the program's)

749
00:34:32,146 --> 00:34:33,506
(voting arrangement,)

750
00:34:33,866 --> 00:34:34,426
(I can't do it.)

751
00:34:34,506 --> 00:34:35,186
(No, no.)

752
00:34:35,186 --> 00:34:36,066
(It's not that exaggerated.)

753
00:34:36,066 --> 00:34:37,266
(Just follow the script.)

754
00:34:37,586 --> 00:34:38,866
(Our script is very clear.)

755
00:34:38,866 --> 00:34:40,266
(Just read it as it is, right?)

756
00:34:40,266 --> 00:34:40,506
(So...)

757
00:34:40,986 --> 00:34:41,626
(So simple.)

758
00:34:41,626 --> 00:34:43,026
(This is a competitive show.)

759
00:34:43,826 --> 00:34:45,786
(I can only vote
according to the rules of the show,)

760
00:34:46,026 --> 00:34:47,306
(for the audience and the contestants.)

761
00:34:47,306 --> 00:34:47,746
(Yes.)

762
00:34:47,746 --> 00:34:48,506
(But)

763
00:34:48,506 --> 00:34:50,226
(we have discussed this many times,)

764
00:34:50,226 --> 00:34:50,706
(haven't we?)

765
00:34:50,826 --> 00:34:52,266
(Don't make it difficult for me.)

766
00:34:52,266 --> 00:34:53,706
(Please don't put me
in a difficult position.)

767
00:34:53,706 --> 00:34:55,746
(It's hard for me
to explain to the higher-ups.)

768
00:34:56,146 --> 00:34:56,826
(Don't hassle me.)

769
00:34:56,826 --> 00:34:57,626
What are you watching?

770
00:34:58,666 --> 00:34:59,306
(Mr. Heisha.)

771
00:34:59,506 --> 00:35:01,106
Have you seen this video?

772
00:35:01,506 --> 00:35:02,506
(So, are you paying for this?)

773
00:35:03,266 --> 00:35:04,546
