786
00:35:44,426 --> 00:35:45,506
Work overtime again?

787
00:35:46,346 --> 00:35:47,506
I'm serious.

788
00:35:48,706 --> 00:35:50,266
I've been thinking recently,

789
00:35:51,186 --> 00:35:52,266
in fact, in this world,

790
00:35:52,266 --> 00:35:53,746
