each other's imperfections,

793
00:35:58,666 --> 00:36:01,026
accompany each other

794
00:36:02,186 --> 00:36:03,306
and then grow together.

795
00:36:06,266 --> 00:36:07,186
This should be

796
00:36:07,186 --> 00:36:08,426
the most important thing

797
00:36:08,586 --> 00:36:09,706
in Fragment Time Boyfriend.

798
00:36:13,746 --> 00:36:15,586
Miss An Ran speaks really well.

799
00:36:16,866 --> 00:36:17,506
But

800
00:36:20,106 --> 00:36:20,986
